title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Disk Groups
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the disk groups of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system: the fault-tolerance
 status, RAID level, member and spare counts and any running background job. A
 verify or scrub is treated as normal maintenance; a reconstruct is alertable.

 State is taken from the disk-group status reported by the array. Conditions
 are configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 disk group" ruleset.

item:
 The disk group name (for example {"dgA01"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per disk group.
